{"tid":2355751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃馮律師行遭接管｜I.T男賣舊樓套400萬換新樓 恐被發展商殺訂120萬兼捱貴租","createTime":"2021-01-06T09:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:12:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"89267c26bdb61a5a7a64c52bf5c6e8a38d2cc870","tid":2355751,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"黃馮律師行作為行內處理二手樓買賣合約的「一哥」，不少客戶都是因為地產經紀介紹或銀行規定而選用黃馮，今年40多歲的Ken就是其中一個。「我原先打算換樓，舊樓已賣套現咗400幾萬，於12月21日當日存放於黃馮，原定28日成交，29、30日就可以收樓。」做電腦行業，一心希望改善家人生活的Ken，賣出舊樓後以900多萬買入大埔樓花，本先年尾就開心收樓，誰知400多萬突然被凍結，現時正透過新的律師代表與發展商溝通，希望可以延遲交易。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772344_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772344_0&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=2c39eafc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772344_0&h=1b6134c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772344_0</a>"},{"pid":"01d2b0abe286d1824fae0b13de473131d6aff4bc","tid":2355751,"uid":136797,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"殺佢大訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢家市好可以加價推"},{"pid":"6b54e7b435d5a033dc6708c3702840d00e52f97b","tid":2355751,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"就咁睇覺得換自住樓係件好危險既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c061d956ca9616b1788cce126432e55c11b973b","tid":2355751,"uid":145690,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"01d2b0abe286d1824fae0b13de473131d6aff4bc","tid":2355751,"uid":136797,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"殺佢大訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\